5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Related to sales and use tax; to exempt the Auxiliary
10 of Big Oak Ranch, Incorporated, from the payment or collection
11 of state sales and use taxes; and to allow municipalities and
12 counties to exempt this entity from local sales and use
13 taxes.
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
15 Section 1. (a) The Auxiliary of Big Oak Ranch,
16 Incorporated, is exempt from paying or collecting any state
17 sales and use taxes.
18 (b) Any county or municipality may exempt the entity
19 from the payment or collection of county or municipal sales
20 and use taxes in accordance with Section 40-23-4.01, Code of
21 Alabama 1975.
22 Section 2. This act shall become effective on September
23 1, 2026.
